OL,3,CHome Office has chance to end 'failed'
OL,4,Casylum accommodation system, MPs say
OL,6,FMinisters must set out a clear
OL,7,Fstrategy of how to reduce the use of
OL,8,Fasylum hotels and have a chance to end
OL,9,Fthe "current failed, chaotic and
OL,10,Fexpensive" system that has wasted
OL,11,Ftaxpayers' money, a committee of MPs
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe Government has promised to end the
OL,15,Fhousing of asylum seekers in hotels by
OL,16,F2029 amid mounting pressure over
OL,17,Frising costs and a backlash in local
OL,18,Fcommunities.
