OL,3,CHome Office has chance to end 'failed'
OL,4,Casylum accommodation system, MPs say
OL,6,FBut the Home Affairs Committee has
OL,7,Fwarned a promise to appeal to popular
OL,8,Fopinion without a clear plan for
OL,9,Falternative accommodation risks "under-
OL,10,Fdelivery and consequently undermining
OL,11,Fpublic trust still further".
OL,13,FA report published on Monday said the
OL,14,FHome Office has failed to share a long-
OL,15,Fterm strategy for asylum seeker
OL,16,Faccommodation and repeatedly cut
OL,17,Fcorners in its "chaotic" response to
OL,18,Fthe pressures.
