OL,3,CHome Office has chance to end 'failed'
OL,4,Casylum accommodation system, MPs say
OL,6,FExpected costs of Home Office
OL,7,Faccommodation contracts for 2019-2029
OL,8,Fhave since tripled from #4.5 billion
OL,9,Fto #15.3 billion, after a "dramatic
OL,10,Fincrease" in demand following the
OL,11,Fpandemic and rising numbers of those
OL,12,Farriving by small boat among the
OL,13,Ffactors.
OL,15,FThe report said: "The Home Office has
OL,16,Fundoubtedly been operating in an
OL,17,Fextremely challenging environment but
OL,18,Fits chaotic response has demonstrated
OL,19,Fthat it has not been up to the
OL,20,Fchallenge.
