OL,3,CHome Office has chance to end 'failed'
OL,4,Casylum accommodation system, MPs say
OL,6,F"The 2026 break clause and end of the
OL,7,Fcontracts in 2029 represent
OL,8,Fopportunities to draw a line under the
OL,9,Fcurrent failed, chaotic and expensive
OL,10,Fsystem and move to a model that is
OL,11,Fmore effective and offers value for
OL,12,Fmoney."
OL,14,FAsylum hotels became a focal point
OL,15,Fover the summer with multiple
OL,16,Fdemonstrations particularly centred
OL,17,Faround the Bell Hotel in Epping, where
OL,18,Fan asylum seeker was charged and later
OL,19,Fjailed for sexual assault.
