OL,4,Casylum accommodation system, MPs say
OL,6,FThe MPs' report added that protests at
OL,7,Fasylum sites have involved local
OL,8,Fresidents with "genuine concerns", as
OL,9,Fwell as people travelling from other
OL,10,Fareas "to promote divisive agendas or
OL,11,Finstigate disorder".
OL,13,FMPs pressed for the Home Office to
OL,14,Fprioritise closing hotels where there
OL,15,Fhave been "significant community
OL,16,Fcohesion issues", as well as hotels in
OL,17,Fremote areas that can place the most
OL,18,Fpressure on local services.
