OL,3,CHome Office has chance to end 'failed'
OL,4,Casylum accommodation system, MPs say
OL,6,FThe committee said the Home Office's
OL,7,Ffailure to engage with communities has
OL,8,Fled to missed opportunities to address
OL,9,Flocal concerns.
OL,11,FThe report added: "The lack of
OL,12,Fengagement and transparency has left
OL,13,Fspace for misinformation and mistrust
OL,14,Fto grow, which in too many areas has
OL,15,Fled to tensions and undermined the
OL,16,Fability of local partners to promote
OL,17,Fsocial cohesion."
