OL,3,CHome Office has chance to end 'failed'
OL,4,Casylum accommodation system, MPs say
OL,6,FThe report detailed how the
OL,7,FGovernment's approach has led to an
OL,8,Funeven distribution of asylum
OL,9,Faccommodation around the country,
OL,10,Foften concentrated in areas of high
OL,11,Fdeprivation.
OL,13,FThe committee called for a future
OL,14,Faccommodation system to be based on
OL,15,Ffairness rather than cost alone,
OL,16,Fimprove communication with local
OL,17,Fcommunities and be flexible to meet
OL,18,Funpredictable demands.
