OL,3,CHome Office has chance to end 'failed'
OL,4,Casylum accommodation system, MPs say
OL,6,F"The Home Office has not proved able
OL,7,Fto develop a long-term strategy for
OL,8,Fthe delivery of asylum accommodation.
OL,9,FIt has instead focused on short-term,
OL,10,Freactive responses.
OL,12,F"The Home Office must finally learn
OL,13,Ffrom its previous mistakes or it is
OL,14,Fdoomed to repeat them."
OL,16,FThe report also raised how the
OL,17,Fdepartment neglected its day-to-day
OL,18,Fmanagement of the contracts, and had
OL,19,Fnot sufficiently ordered financial
OL,20,Fpenalties for providers who have poor
OL,21,Fperformance.
