OL,6,FThe charity's head of advocacy, Sile
OL,7,FReynolds, said: "Everyday Freedom from
OL,8,FTorture therapists see first-hand the
OL,9,Fdevastating impact that hotels,
OL,10,Fmilitary sites and shared bedrooms
OL,11,Fhave on people who came to this
OL,12,Fcountry seeking safety.
OL,14,F"Living in fear, without privacy,
OL,15,Fstability, or access to proper
OL,16,Fhealthcare, strips people of their
OL,17,Fdignity and undermines their recovery.
